{"tid":2362300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國人聽著，Trump內閣而家一定要聽連登仔意見總辭同埋唔好再選總統","createTime":"2021-01-11T10:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T11:02:56.000Z","uid":142888,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fef14dc398225c298af005fa87193f862bcf60fd","tid":2362300,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"今次侵被滅聲同成堆共和黨背叛反映美國體制嘅腐敗，Trump應該立即同其內閣總閣。體制內鬥爭已經冇用，反而會俾建制派合法性。<br />\n<br />\n有好多幾次FOX news都唔支持侵，正一同香港嘅垃場新聞同毒果一樣嚮到玩中立，所有侵粉應該立即唔好再睇<br />\n<br />\n對於未來嘅抗爭，我哋唯有玩焦土同加速主義，寧願投俾美共Antifa都唔投俾共和黨。最後民主黨會係Antifa同美共嘅condom。<br />\n<br />\n其實我見到侵本人同咁多侵粉被打壓真係好開心，因為呢個證明攬炒成功。又送咗好多子彈俾英國佬巴西佬，我幾驚佢哋唔打壓，加速主義好！"},{"pid":"13a7433666f21a6c5083c147979c809263768063","tid":2362300,"uid":353981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"你當你自己係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbed737ad48908e138096af6f0c4c57b198695da","tid":2362300,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"墨西哥總統反對Twitter封Trump係想食美國侵粉人血饅頭"},{"pid":"4326e6208ef8f4e4c16e489657d2ace68a3c53bf","tid":2362300,"uid":200280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MBe9r0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MBe9r0.png&h=78a81558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDKDRGf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDKDRGf.png&h=a0041b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W33tusW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW33tusW.png&h=7bb7d2ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08926ec714ce90f92e07ead943e5044fb056205d","tid":2362300,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"依家trump 都仲未落台已經打人打壓到咁<br />\n落埋台唔知會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surpris